bsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115969)\">D&amp;C 124:38-41<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">15. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110842\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110842)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110842)\">Rev. 19:10<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">16. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106589\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106589)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106589)\">Job 9:20<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106595\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106595)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106595)\">Job 15:6<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108562\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108562)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108562)\">Luke 19:22<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">17. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108193\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108193)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108193)\">Matt. 23:37<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">18. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115982\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115982)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115982)\">D&amp;C 124:39-40<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">19. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116005\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116005)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116005)\">D&amp;C 124:55<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">20. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116404\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116404)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116404)\">D&amp;C 132:28-33<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">21. \